OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FRising electricity demand from data
OL,7,Fcentres is "offsetting gains in
OL,8,Frenewable generation", a climate
OL,9,Fwatchdog has warned.
OL,11,FThe annual review from the Climate
OL,12,FChange Advisory Council said limited
OL,13,Fadditional capacity from renewable
OL,14,Fenergy leaves Ireland "unnecessarily
OL,15,Fdependent on imported fossil fuels and
OL,16,Fexposed to global energy shocks".
OL,18,FThe review outlines that emissions in
OL,19,Fthe electricity sector fell by around
OL,20,F8% in 2025 compared with 2024.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@UO]vD@WOUxD@`O]
