OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FTargets were missed for the share of
OL,7,Felectricity demand met by renewable
OL,8,Fsources, with rising data centre
OL,9,Fdemand eroding improvements in
OL,10,Frenewable generation.
OL,12,FThe review says Ireland's electricity
OL,13,Fdemand rose by 2.6% in 2025, outpacing
OL,14,Fthe annual European increase of 1%,
OL,15,Fand is now 30.2% higher than in 2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FThat growth is almost entirely driven
OL,7,Fby data centre expansion in Ireland,
OL,8,Fwith data centres experiencing an
OL,9,Faverage year-on-year growth rate of
OL,10,F23% since 2015, while all other Irish
OL,11,Fcustomer demand has increased by 0.5%
OL,12,Fper annum on average during the same
OL,13,Fperiod.
OL,15,FThis means that, using the latest
OL,16,FCentral Statistics Office (CSO) data,
OL,17,Fconsumption directly from data centres
OL,18,Fhas risen by 463% since records began
OL,19,Fin 2015 and by 220% since 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
