OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FThe review says: "As new renewable
OL,7,Fdeployment has ultimately been matched
OL,8,For exceeded by increasing data centre
OL,9,Fdemand, recent reductions in
OL,10,Felectricity sector emissions are
OL,11,Flargely driven by a substantial
OL,12,Fincrease in net electricity imports
OL,13,Fand the reduction in coal-fired power
OL,14,Fgeneration."
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
