FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FAlex White, chairman of the Climate
OL,7,FChange Advisory Council, said
OL,8,Frenewable energy "helps to reduce
OL,9,Fwholesale electricity prices" but
OL,10,FIrish homes "will not feel the full
OL,11,Fbenefit unless we build the grid,
OL,12,Fstorage and capacity needed to use
OL,13,Fthat power".
OL,15,F"Every year of delay leaves Ireland
OL,16,Fmore exposed to imported fossil fuels,
OL,17,Fvolatile global markets and avoidable
OL,18,Fcosts," he said.
OL,26,@pD@ROUqD@]O]rD@MOUuD@KO]wD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
