OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,F"Storm Eowyn showed how vulnerable our
OL,7,Felectricity system, essential services
OL,8,Fand communities remain to extreme
OL,9,Fweather.
OL,11,F"Electricity resilience must be
OL,12,Fcentral to national climate adaptation
OL,13,Fplanning, with clear responsibility,
OL,14,Finvestment and delivery.
OL,16,F"The Government has set the right
OL,17,Fambition to end Ireland's reliance on
OL,18,Ffossil fuels. The test now is delivery.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,F"Critical grid projects must be
OL,7,Fprioritised, renewable planning must
OL,8,Fbe accelerated, and the benefits of
OL,9,Fclean electricity must reach Irish
OL,10,Fhouseholds and business to ensure
OL,11,Fenergy security and affordability for
OL,12,Fall."
OL,14,FThe body is calling for urgent action
OL,15,Fto accelerate renewable electricity
OL,16,Fdelivery, particularly onshore wind
OL,17,Fand solar.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
