PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778637819
OL,3,CRising data centre demand offsetting
OL,4,Cgreen power gains, watchdog warns
OL,6,FIt says the Critical Infrastructure
OL,7,FBill must designate electricity grid
OL,8,Freinforcement projects for prioritised
OL,9,Fdelivery and must not remove the
OL,10,Fclimate obligations that apply to all
OL,11,Fpublic bodies under Irish law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
